div.p:
The following were present at the 152d meeting of the Council: The President of
                    the United States, Presiding; the Vice President of the United States;
                        Richard M. Nixon. the
                    Acting Secretary of State;
                        Walter Bedell Smith. the
                    Acting Secretary of Defense;
                        Roger M. Kyes. the Director
                    for Mutual Security;
                        Harold E. Stassen. the
                    Director, Office of Defense Mobilization.
                        Arthur S. Flemming.
                    Also present were the Secretary of the Treasury;
                        George M. Humphrey. the
                    Attorney General (for Item 1);
                        Herbert Brownell, Jr.
                     the Director, Bureau of the Budget;
                        Joseph M. Dodge. the
                    United States Representative to the United Nations
                        Henry Cabot Lodge, Jr.
                     (for Item 6); the Chairman, Joint Chiefs of Staff;
                        General of the Army Omar N.
                            Bradley. the Director of Central Intelligence;
                        Allen W. Dulles.
                    Robert Cutler, Special Assistant to
                    the President; C.D. Jackson,
                    Special Assistant to the President; the Military Liaison Officer; the Acting
                    Executive Secretary, NSC; and Hugh D.
                        Farley, NSC Special Staff
                    Member.
